SUMMARY: Have you ever dreamed of giving it all up, leaving it all behind and hitting the road to escape all your responsibilities?

TITLE: Afghan women protest outside Kabul University as male students return to class
SUMMARY: Young Afghan women gathered outside Kabul University on Monday to protest the ruling Taliban's ban on female education as their male peers returned to school for a new academic year and the United Nations heard the restriction may amount to a crime against humanity.

TITLE: Thailand jails five poachers for killing tiger and her cub
SUMMARY: A court in western Thailand on Monday sentenced five poachers to prison terms of five years each for killing a female tiger and her cub in a national park last year.

TITLE: Japan's new rocket fails on debut launch in setback for space program
SUMMARY: Japan's maiden launch of its new flagship space rocket ended in failure on Tuesday when controllers issued a destruct command just 15 minutes after liftoff, the country's space agency said.

TITLE: Explosion of sea lion deaths in Peru amid deadly bird flu outbreak
SUMMARY: Thousands of sea lions have died in Peru amid an outbreak of bird flu, according to Peru's National Service of Protected Areas by the State (SERNANP).

TITLE: US adds Chinese genetics firms to trade blacklist over surveillance allegations
SUMMARY: The United States on Thursday added two subsidiaries of Chinese genetics company BGI to a trade blacklist over allegations it conducted genetic analysis and surveillance activities for Beijing, which Washington says was used to repress ethnic minorities in China.

The Italian brand unveiled its Fall-Winter 2023 collection against a backdrop of over 200,000 Durex boxes, nodding to both sex positivity and a forthcoming collaboration with the contraceptive company.

TITLE: Unpleasant truth about air travel's 'golden age'
